members.member:
Base class for both the compress and decompress classes.
Holds common arrays, and static data.

@author Keiron Liddle

An input stream that decompresses from the BZip2 format (with the file header chars) to be read as any other stream.
@author Keiron Liddle
NB: note this class has been modified to read the leading BZ from the start of the BZIP2 stream to make it compatible with other PGP programs.

An output stream that compresses into the BZip2 format (with the file header chars) into another stream.
@author Keiron Liddle
TODO: Update to BZip2 1.0.1 NB: note this class has been modified to add a leading BZ to the start of the BZIP2 stream to make it compatible with other PGP programs.

A simple class the hold and calculate the CRC for sanity checking
of the data.

@author Keiron Liddle

